lead_paragraph: By the arrival of the bark Chase, Capt. CHASE, at this port from Turks Island 13th September, we have received files of Grand Turk papers to the loth ult:. In consequence of many vessels having lately arrived at Turks Island in ballast, while the Provision markets 'continue to give remunerative prices;
